{
  "stem": "15396.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And as I got to the door to go through on the way to Spain, I looked back and they were passing them around and laughing and all, and all I wanted to do was jump in there and click my heels, and-- and-- then I went to Barcelona.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was coming out of-- I had some messages for the British consulate.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I came out of the consulate and was arrested and taken into occupied France.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some policemen.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the French-- the Spaniards were not very-- individually, were not pro-Nazi.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the-- officially they were supposed to cooperate a little bit.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In this particular case, there were some who did.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We never knew who they were.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know if they were Spaniards or what.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But anyway, I was waiting in this bench with several other people to be interrogated, with my bags there-- trumpet in a little bag there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I saw this officer coming out with a-- with a collaborator hanging on him, on his arm, you know, talking to him and trying to convince him of something.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And, you know, they hated the collaborators, as you can imagine, more than anything.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so, I don't know what-- you know, adrenaline is a fantastic thing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Suddenly I jumped up and opened the door for them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then I reached back and took my two cases, the trumpet and the case, and followed them out the door, and then out the courtyard, and then out the gate.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And everybody thought I was carrying their luggage.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Except they didn't, because they were talking.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I was far enough behind them so that-- and I was also acting it up pretty well.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And when we got out, then I-- I hitchhiked later.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
